    Class Description
    OMAAccessUnitFormatBox  
    OMACommonHeadersBox  
    OMAContentIDBox
    The ContentID box contains the unique identifier for the Content Object the metadata are associated with.
    OMAContentObjectBox  
    OMADiscreteMediaHeadersBox
    The Discrete Media headers box includes fields specific to the DCF format and the Common Headers box, followed by an optional user-data box.
    OMARightsObjectBox
    The rights object box may be used to insert a Protected Rights Object, defined in 'OMA DRM v2.1' section 5.3.9, into a DCF or PDCF.
    OMATransactionTrackingBox
    The OMA DRM Transaction Tracking Box enables transaction tracking as defined in 'OMA DRM v2.1' section 15.3.
    OMAURLBox
    This box is used for several sub-boxes of the user-data box in an OMA DRM file.
